movie.title: Unstoppable
movie.plot: A runaway train carrying a cargo of toxic chemicals puts an engineer and his conductor in a race against time. They're chasing the runaway train in a separate locomotive and need to bring it under control before it derails on a curve and causes a toxic spill that will decimate a town.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 1 win & 13 nominations.
